Stage Book Title / Type	Symbolizes
Baby/Toddler	Coloring Book	Creativity, early discovery
Child	ABC & Math Workbook	Learning, structure
Teen	Journal / Diary	Identity, emotions, independence
Adult	File Folder / Portfolio	Career, contribution, ambition
Senior	Memory Book / Album	Reflection, life’s journey

